{"tid":120853,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人左邊膊頭裡面嘅唔知筋定骨好痛","createTime":"2017-02-14T17:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T16:32:56.000Z","uid":55514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4263102cfe3efbfe8eeba326510a5661e8dddf15","tid":120853,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲人，痛左幾年<br />\n唔知關唔關睡姿(打側訓)或者打飛機事<br />\n上網睇又話咩心臟有事(會唔會係成日夜訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n有冇巴打都係咁"},{"pid":"e32389243e3d4e137f9b9cce8bd99c99abfa0648","tid":120853,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:40:47.000Z","msg":"我都係，我懷疑係打機個姿勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29292d938483c5e64a02b081dd6b4cadac40ca8d","tid":120853,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係，我懷疑係打機個姿勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係沿住鎖骨摸上膀頭個骨頂隔離個凹位，入邊條根痛"},{"pid":"64a2d54afd5ff004d2548ea93029a6d7d94580af","tid":120853,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係，我懷疑係打機個姿勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係沿住鎖骨摸上膀頭個骨頂隔離個凹位，入邊條根痛</blockquote><br />\n諗緊會唔會係筋膜炎，不過諗左幾年都未睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b2b175eb4347d57750e6b99b8c1c06e718e1ff","tid":120853,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df96f970676daa9ed9a3a5618fe33f2cf4032c97","tid":120853,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間唔中 一個星期會有一野膊頭入面好似比枝好撚粗既針插穿左咁痛撚到仆街<br />\n由細到大都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有時會，你會唔會係啲骨崎形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dbf6fef3de7c5eb6c2d40de68a4700c20be2bb","tid":120853,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:47:51.000Z","msg":"一樣左頸膊果d位傷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76bd5ff13230e5d97adcfb773000d7d88126d38","tid":120853,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣左頸膊果d位傷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過醫?"},{"pid":"f94640498b5893e05a36d0142078f263806451d2","tid":120853,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一樣左頸膊果d位傷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過醫?</blockquote><br />\n醫左好耐都係間唔中會痛<br />\n幾千蚊啦"},{"pid":"5cd121173fb993c9f2168b4455f065ed8022eea6","tid":120853,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T18:47:09.000Z","msg":"胸鎖乳突肌？好多孭得野多都會疲勞"},{"pid":"a0a53ac7c18dd0378bf9609ec6349742472dffbd","tid":120853,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T01:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一樣左頸膊果d位傷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過醫?</blockquote><br />\n醫左好耐都係間唔中會痛<br />\n幾千蚊啦</blockquote><br />\n咁貴架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedd4252e6e70da7ba37b8aba6b6f1ede4aa7d9b","tid":120853,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T01:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胸鎖乳突肌？好多孭得野多都會疲勞</blockquote><br />\ngoogle過應該唔係，btw thank you巴打"},{"pid":"7630f1901903c51fa7fa94ed7051ff5fd5181202","tid":120853,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T02:01:14.000Z","msg":"兩邊膊頭從來無鬆過<br />\n硬過石頭, 次