22:10:01.000Z","msg":"長年舊患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 左右腳都有，但左邊勁啲。<br />\n個感覺就好似入面好空，行下個關節都會好痛<br />\n睇過醫生話係炎症黎"},{"pid":"decdb70ca53412470f55530fed641b61f4d12043","tid":120853,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:54:47.000Z","msg":"之前都試過，無搞佢幾日就好番<br />\n愈搞愈痛"},{"pid":"b4430448c3dfda2d1210f6c1ccb26a8650838533","tid":120853,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:55:23.000Z","msg":"摸落去好似條筋咁，係咪？"},{"pid":"d93bca586bf2f7e20171eb72dd4c80a72901a435","tid":120853,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:56:26.000Z","msg":"我間唔中會有種「拍」一下既感覺，之後個邊隻手有一秒係完全無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b766596d69cc1a0abc00ae7db85b1428b48d398","tid":120853,"uid":48046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:59:08.000Z","msg":"膊頭好難就咁討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太多Structures啦<br />\n巴打想醫嘅就去睇下物理治療啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有巴打提到好似比針一下拮落去咁  或者好似夾左一下咁都可能係impingenent<br />\n而你覺得好明顯係一條筋嘅話就去睇下好啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}